</span><span class='line'>// &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>@media (max-width: 767px) {
</span><span class='line'>  // GRID &amp; CONTAINERS
</span><span class='line'>  // &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&ndash;
</span><span class='line'>  // Remove width from containers
</span><span class='line'>  .container {&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;pre>&lt;code>width: auto;
</span><span class='line'>padding: 0 20px;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>  }
</span><span class='line'>  // Fluid rows
</span><span class='line'>  .row-fluid {&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;pre>&lt;code>width: 100%;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>  }
</span><span class='line'>  // Undo negative margin on rows
</span><span class='line'>  .row {&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;pre>&lt;code>margin-left: 0;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>  }
</span><span class='line'>  // Make all columns even
</span><span class='line'>  .row > [class&lt;em>=&ldquo;span&rdquo;],
</span><span class='line'>  .row-fluid > [class&lt;/em>=&ldquo;span&rdquo;] {&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;pre>&lt;code>float: none;
</span><span class='line'>display: block;
</span><span class='line'>width: auto;
</span><span class='line'>margin: 0;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>  }
</span><span class='line'>}&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p></span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>This is a small part in responsive.less. As we can see, it use the media query to apply the propriate style for device.
On the device that max-width is under 767px, like LANDSCAPE Phone and PORTRAIT TABLET, container width will be set to auto,
and the span width will be set to full width to display propally on device. For example:</p>

